    "description": "来自北方的侵略者就快要达到村子了，侵略者的大军追赶着帝国的溃军，帝国的溃军追赶着路上的土匪和森林里的妖精，她们依次来到村子，企图大肆劫掠。<br>你需要协助村卫队抵抗这些对村子图谋不轨的坏蛋，并最终在侵略者大军到来前决定是撤离还是坚守村子。<br>你也许觉得土匪也就罢了，区区一个小村子怎么可能抵御庞大的军队？不用担心，你可以用钱资助村子学者雨女的研究，获得各种先进武器。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/3897c4d4d3fc4bc76bdc2b781f5598f3.poster.avif?t=1724146927\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/3897c4d4d3fc4bc76bdc2b781f5598f3.webm?t=1724146927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/3897c4d4d3fc4bc76bdc2b781f5598f3.mp4?t=1724146927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>不过，你也可以仅靠自己的实力，成为剑术大师，利用闪避格挡和反击，一个人单挑侵略者大军。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/21a532728b7d8e9e65d332d3a225ee72.poster.avif?t=1724146927\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/21a532728b7d8e9e65d332d3a225ee72.webm?t=1724146927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/21a532728b7d8e9e65d332d3a225ee72.mp4?t=1724146927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>甚至，你可以利用村子的建筑，巧妙地伏击闯入村子的侵略者，村子的房屋大都用稻草和木材建成的，容易着火。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140410/extras/82c641ce6ae3b3427325ea18d77a7efd.avif?t=1724146927\" width=380 height=308 /></span>",
